@Taylor Dent, 
Cooking pizza with cast iron is epic. When using cast iron you usually want to use a dutch oven, that is have a lid that can absorb heat as well.
my suggestion is to heat the cast iron first and with a peel drop the pizza into the pan so you can use the heat of the pan to do the cooking, and, make it well covered with a lid of some sort, any pan / lid is better than foil and it should work well.
